<h2 id="lec-1---basic-structure-of-electrochemical-cells">Lec 1 - Basic Structure of Electrochemical Cells</h2>

<h4 id="trivia">Trivia</h4>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">1 ùëíùëâ \sim 1.6 √ó 10^{‚àí19} C/electron √ó 1ùëâ √ó 6.02 √ó 10^{23} electron/mole = 96.4 kJ/mole</script>

<p>this value is called Faraday‚Äôs constant, $F$.</p>

<h4 id="cell-notation">Cell notation</h4>

